The following components in [salt/modules/mandrill.py](https://github.com/saltstack/salt/blob/master/salt/modules/mandrill.py) have been deprecated, and have a `warn_until()` message specifying `Sodium`.

https://github.com/saltstack/salt/blob/1a5ce828ad983e15205a80ae361150069afaebac/salt/modules/mandrill.py#L127-L228

This was included in the output of a query using the following `grep` command from root of the repo:

```
grep -Rn "warn_until" -A1 | egrep -i "Magnesium|Sodium" | egrep -v "_build|salt.7|deprecations.rst"
```